{"tid":612354,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"一人n個發過恐怖嘅惡夢","createTime":"2018-03-31T18:45:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-31T19:33:37.000Z","uid":39024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"bd02e45b3ffe0119117f02ed2792b12d605ca53d","tid":612354,"uid":39024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T18:45:49.000Z","msg":"今晚第一個夢入面嘅男主角本來同一家大細食緊飯 <br />\n突然有個人send sms過嚟叫佢落街幫佢喺車尾箱攞啲嘢<br />\n咁個主角就走落樓見佢 一路聽佢講架車有幾多嘢 一路等佢開車尾箱 男主屋企人就喺側邊望住<br />\n<br />\n原本大家仲有說有笑 點知一打開發現係條屍<br />\n轉個頭個人就唔見咗 <br />\n<br />\n成家好驚惶嘅時候 男主再次收到message<br />\n&lsquo;Take care of the body.&rsquo;"},{"pid":"16feef643cc16d19c00d2f2bc3b944b5a6b1b463","tid":612354,"uid":39024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T18:47:45.000Z","msg":"唔知各位巴絲會唔會 <br />\n我自己一晚會發成五至十個夢 有長有短 好多醒返都會記得或者有印象<br />\n搞到日日瞓醒都好攰 好似廿四小時無休息過不停活動咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n正正常常嗰啲夢 或者科幻啲 刺激啲都冇乜嘢 有時仲發得幾開心<br />\n不過一發惡夢就好大鑊 有時控制到自己 知道自己發緊夢 但有時真係分唔到現實同夢境<br />\n<br />\n今日發嘅呢幾個係一連串嘅 我原本都控制到 可以好似睇戲咁睇<br />\n仲安排咗啲劇情發生喺同一個世界<br />\n點知去到最尾所有嘢突然間發生喺我身上 就嚇醒咗<br />\n而家先嗰兩點半 唔敢再瞓了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8be0b96f8912c758e6e2de4a92b126ae86b7c620","tid":612354,"uid":155702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T18:50:04.000Z","msg":"當打機咁囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好少發惡夢<br />\n利申唔識安慰人"},{"pid":"eff2188bedc3ecc87dda49450a00ccfeb9ba6db2","tid":612354,"uid":69759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T18:52:21.000Z","msg":"有好多鬼衝落我到<br />\n就算我知係夢都醒唔到 唯有面對<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n衝哂先醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c2463cf970c7bab8dcfb9281bd21a06f2773bdf","tid":612354,"uid":176763,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T18:52:49.000Z","msg":"最恐怖係係現實發生嘅情景曾經係夢入面出現過"},{"pid":"fc06ede53379caba96d0e4fbb042240a8a1d28d8","tid":612354,"uid":143915,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T18:53:28.000Z","msg":"係高層跌落街<br />\n有離心力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c7676d99458db3d2bae6bd8f35f2e5e249c9eb3","tid":612354,"uid":39024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8be0b96f8912c758e6e2de4a92b126ae86b7c620","tid":612354,"uid":155702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T18:50:04.000Z","msg":"當打機咁囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好少發惡夢<br />\n利申唔識安慰人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T18:55:01.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但有時啲夢係有埋其他官感<br />\n頭先臨嚇醒之前畀個女人咬我隻手<br />\n打極都唔肯走<br />\n醒返仲係又痛又痹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38068db7fbc18cfffd4eb1db78cc7c18ee4cfabd","tid":612354,"uid":39024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc06ede53379caba96d0e4fbb042240a8a1d28d8","tid":612354,"uid":143915,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T18:53:28.000Z","msg":"係高層跌落街<br />\n有離心力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T18:58:49.000Z","msg":"係呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我本身畏高<br />\n但又成日發埋啲墮樓夢<br />\n醒嗰陣會彈起身<br />\n驚到喊 醒返成個枕頭濕晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26a5700dc39fd0ddacc17787a5300e2df4a316fa","tid":612354,"uid":176166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T19:08:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4197b0020b5735966866bc62e968df7db02d4569","tid":612354,"uid":58140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T19:33:37.000Z","msg":"回魂夜情節 d lift壞左 再行後樓梯見到個著紅衫呀婆係度燒緊衣紙比自己<br />\n個樣勁恐怖 之後我同自己講 假既假既 之後跑落大堂<br />\n但跑極都跑唔完咁 之後就醒左"}]}